Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.86,片头,,0,0,0,,{\blur60\move(0,380,360,380,50,50)}圣诞特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,每年我都得跟皮克维尔小姐解释\NEvery year I'd explain to Miss Pickwell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节就是耶稣基督的诞辰\Nthat the Nativity is about Jesus being born,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是他被鞭打 钉十字架的那天\Nnot him being beaten, whipped and crucified in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 她对犹太人被屠杀也表现出了那么点忧桑\NYeah, she also went a little bit heavy with the Jew-bashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,格林教授是代替她的确定人选 不过她...\NPro Green was a shoe-in to replace her, but she's, er....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在和我爸度蜜月 是的 我再清楚不过了\NOn honeymoon with my dad,yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想忘记那个\NI'm trying not to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的观点就是 除非你亲自出马 不然就没有圣诞剧表演了\NMy point is, there'll be no Xmas play unless you step up to the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 弗瑞泽 我马上就跟你说我为啥不想上场\NOK, Fraser, I'll tell you why I'm not going to do the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也不是这样...\NI was like everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在我小时候 圣诞剧演出是圣诞节的高潮部分\Nwhen I was growing up, Nativities were the highlight of my Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,之后 有一年 我演了一个最棒的角色\NAnd then, one year,I got the best part I'd ever got.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,约瑟?\NJoseph?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,二号小鼹鼠\NMole 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,马槽里有鼹鼠吗?这个嘛 应该有的\NWere there moles in the manger?Er, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是妈妈答应我 她会来看我的演出...\NMy mum promised that she'd come and watch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到我出场的时候 你知道我看到了什么吗?\NAnd I went out on stage,do you know what I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没看到?鼹鼠都是瞎的 才不是...\NNothing? Moles are blind. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈的座位是空的\NMy mum's empty chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,于是那只可怜的小鼹鼠就只想挖个洞钻到地底下 然后消失\NAnd that poor little mole just wanted to burrow down into the ground and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你看哈 你不需要做耶稣诞生表演!\NBut look,you don't have to do a Nativity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们搞一个跨教派表演就行\NIt's time for a non-denominational show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,替"所有的宗教"大声叫好么!\NGive a shout out to "all de religion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可别忘了\NHey, but don't forget mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是信比伯的!\NI'm a Belieber!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 那我就是亵渎比伯之徒\NYeah, well I'm a Bl-atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 从学术上说 我是比伯盲\NActually, technically,I think I'd be Bl-agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 我会骂死他\NI mean, I'd slag him off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他要是能从门外走进来 我就像狗皮膏药似的粘着他\Nbut if he walked in the door now,I'd be all over him like a rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哈!诡计多端的圣诞老人刚刚从他的袋子里掏出了一份大礼呢\NWoo-hoo! Banter Claus just pulled a big one from his gag sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是杀了我算了 我说 你得让史蒂芬参加才行\NKill me. Hey,you've got to get Stephen involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那货可有表演天赋了\NThat guy knows how to put on a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,记不记得他的个人秀《珍爱人生》么?\NRemember his one-man Precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,棒极了!\NSuperb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,《浪人荒原》?\NFiddler on the Heath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,《巡回风暴》\NBarnstorming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有《雪莉·柯尔传》...\NAnd that biopic of Cheryl Cole...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这个有损形象\NLibellous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 我想问 你还记得你用短信发学期末报告这事儿吗?\NAnyhoo, question, remember how you sent your end-of-term reports via text?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 那可是我最有创意的主意之一\NYeah, one of my best ideas ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 我看校领导好像不这么觉得呢\NYeah, well, the school governors don't seem to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙!\NDicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可是一直想让我炒你鱿鱼呢\NThey're quite keen for me to fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要是你肯出演这部圣诞剧\NBut you put on this play,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就保你没事\Nand I'll save your heiney
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让领导们有事都冲我来 护你到底\Nby throwing this ass in front of the governors' spanking hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,成交 我就去演一下你那个破剧\NAll right.I'll do your shitty little play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 还是得告诉你 我讨厌圣诞演出\NBut, just so you know,I hate Christmas shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,提前准备的好东西\NWe have done some perfectly good stuff earlier in the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都派不上用场了 本来节日就够乱了 还得赶着重弄\Nand now we have to ruin it by cobbling together some under-thought through festive bollocks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用一坨坨见鬼的圣诞曲子\Nwith a load of shit Christmas music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谁给我的西汉姆联队赛的门票?\NWho got me a ticket to West Ham?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我誓死支持米尔沃队\NI'm Millwall till I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,投票结果如下 《胡桃夹子》六票 《机器战警》五票\NOK, so six of you have voted for The Nutcracker and five of you have voted for Robocop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要演《胡桃夹子》吗?\NSo we're doing the Nutcracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有人不坚持民主原则了吗?\NOh, someone's changed their tune on democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你别忘了 静 还有我的一票呢\NBut you're forgetting, Jing,I also get a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们到底要演什么?\NSo what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有了\NGot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就演这个了\NThat's our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,《机器小钳子》?\NRobocracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有这种东西吗? 现在还没有 只是现在而已\NDoes that exist?Not yet, my friend. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,神呢 你所谓的剧本是什么 大家再了解不过了\NOh, God,we've read your scripts before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛这副反应?你也不知道细节 不是吗?\NWhat do you mean, "Oh, God"? You don't really do subtlety, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 细节问题会让我发疯的\NEr, subtlety can lick my balls and then eat a plate of my ass for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去维基百科查查 决定情节的混搭问题\NI'll just go on Wikipedia,bosh out a plot mash-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的 不 肯定有用\NThat's not going to work.Er, yes, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最近20年最好的电影的哪部?\NWhat's the best film of the last 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,《电锯惊魂4》《电锯惊魂5》\NSaw 4. Saw 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,《饥饿游戏》《拜见岳父大人》《洛丽塔》\NHunger Games. Meet the Fockers.Lolita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,《尖峰时刻》也不错的 静\NHmm, Rush Hour's a good shout, Jing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过正确的答案是《异形战场》\Nbut the correct answer is Alien Vs Predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,情节的混搭\NA plot mash-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 要是我爸知道我登台表演 他一定会想方设法掐灭我这点儿念头\NMate, if my dad finds out I've been on stage, he'll cut me out the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说你不用继承他那套破破烂烂的运动服了吗?\NSo you won't have to inherit his shitty tracksuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得也是!你也你得不到你妈的衣服 那些可都躺在我的卧室的地板上呢!\NThat makes two of us! You won't be getting your mum's clothes, cos they're all over my bedroom floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,同学们 积点口德 不要问候对方的长辈\NGuys, stop being mean about each other's families.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的爹妈一直给予你们支持和帮助\NYour parents are all so supportive of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你们现在还没什么感觉\NYou might not realise it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你永远不会明白他们有多爱你 直到你的母亲离开...\Nbut you won't appreciate how much they love you, until your mum's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,..去西班牙定居 和哈维尔以及他们的孩子生活在一起\N..to live in Spain,with Javier and their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦!\NGay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 老师\NCome on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你来写剧本 我帮你安排他们试镜\NYou write your masterpiece,I'll help you organise auditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 静\NThanks, Jing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我还忘了说 我们得为所有的教派大声叫好\NOh, and I forgot to say, we have to give a shout out to all the religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,基督教 佛教 伊斯兰教...中国有什么教 静?\NChristianity, Buddhism, Islam...what's China, Jing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数人不信教的 所以你们不过圣诞节吗?\NPredominantly atheists. So, what,you don't get to do Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不公平哎 毕竟玩具都是中国制造\NThat seems a bit unfair considering you make all the toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就好比 圣诞精灵没有圣诞礼物\NThat's like the elves not having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚是在比较...?\NDid you just compare...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说到圣诞礼物 米契尔 格老师的礼物准备好了么?\NOn the subject of presents,Mitchell, how is Miss Gulliver's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我爸特地挑选的 他一哥们儿开了个野驴收容所\NYeah. Dad's sorted it. One of his mates owns a donkey sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你给格老师买了一头驴?让她收养一头驴\NYou're buying Miss Gulliver a donkey? Adopting her a donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 她喜欢动物...而且 驴比雪豹便宜多了\NYou know, she loves animals... and they're a lot cheaper than snow leopards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 再强调一次\NOK, spread the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,预选要开始了 都去找找试镜灵感 好好准备喔\NCasting's at break, so pick your own audition pieces and choose them wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬 今天你准备《霹雳舞》里的那场戏呢?\NOK, Stephen, what scene from Flashdance are you doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,全部 全部?\NAll of it. All of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有一分钟喔 闭嘴看我表演就行\NYou've only got a minute.Just shut up and press play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁呢?\NAnd who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,泽维尔教授 X战警 是不是?\NProfessor Xavier. X-Men, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会读心术 哥们儿\NI can read your mind, bruv.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 哈\NYeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想什么?\NWhat am I thinking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头\NTits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头!\NTits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎么做到的?\NHow does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,仙黛尔 你的灵感来自哪里?\NSo, Chantelle, where have you taken your scene from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,本能\NBasic Instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,本能...?\NBasic Instinct...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我凑!别动!\NOh, my God! Do not move your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显 你还沉浸在自己的剧里呢 真是难以置信\NObviously, you're in the play.That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就他了\NSorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是有一名好演员的\NWe still only have one good actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你就看着那个好点\NYeah, that's all you need.One good one,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就不知道其他的多惨不忍睹\Nthen you don't realise how terrible the other ones actually are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟卡戴珊似的 是吗?没错 当三联画正好\NIt's like the Kardashians. Really?Yeah, as a triptych, fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过把金排除在外\NBut you take Kim out of the equation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,考特尼似乎应该坐在桥底下 守着桥啃山羊\NKourtney suddenly looks like she should be sat underneath a bridge that she guards, eating goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 弗兰克 没必要这么严肃...\NNow, look, Frank,there's no need to take the piss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我来试镜了 不是么?\NI've come to audition, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的舞蹈 半好半坏吧\NYour dance was, like, good and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真谢谢你啊 亲\NOh, thanks, babes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 我没事的\NOh, whatever, man. I'm not bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 好吧... 该你表演了\NWell, OK, um... in your own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个表演可能会很精彩呢 静\NThis is going to be perfect, Jing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他会是我们的B计划 虽然喜怒无常 但是个表演天才\NHe'll be like Plan B, all moody but with an amazing talent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大隐于市 偶尔会露面\Nhidden between the urban, slightly stabby facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的罗密欧呢?\NWhere is my Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?一只杯子 紧紧地握住在我的忠心的爱人的手里?\NWhat's here?A cup, closed in my love's true hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 一定是毒药结果了他的生命\NPoison, I see,hath been his timeless end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像在大便似的\NHe sounds like he's taking a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要吻着你的嘴唇...\NI will kiss thy lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 就到这儿吧\NOK, right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...所以 也有演得不错的地方\NEr...so, let's start with the positives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,音量\NVolume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,声音非常洪亮啊\NIt was very loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我每个词都听得清清楚楚 我确实在想 整个赫特福德郡\NI heard every word, as I think did the whole of Hertfordshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要演什么角色?\NSo what part am I going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾地说 弗兰克 我们已经有足够多的优秀的演员了\NEr, unfortunately, Frank, there are a lot of really great actors out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么角色?很遗憾地说 你落选...\NWhat part? I'm afraid,there isn't a role for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么...角色?\NWhat... part?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,主演?什么?联袂主演\NThe lead? What? The co-lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就跟在《尖峰时刻》里那样\NYes, like in Rush Hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 静\NThanks, Jing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,救得好\NNice save.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好么 老师?\NYou all right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不错啊 你呢?\NI'm snow-K, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也还好\NYeah, not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己呢?\NYours-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁道夫等圣诞老人的鹿!\NOh, Rudolph, Donner,Blitzen and Banter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能把威克斯老师母亲的电话给我吗?\NCan I get Mr Wickers' mum's number,please, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在厕所的墙上写着呢 我试过那个了 打不通\NIt's on the toilet wall. Yeah,I tried that one. It weren't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你为啥想要那个呢?我给威克斯老师准备了一个惊喜\NSorry, why do you want it?I'm arranging Mr Wickers a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是惊喜?毕竟是圣诞节嘛\NGenuinely nice? Yeah.It's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让您邀请她去看威克斯老师的表演 哦!\NI want to invite her to Mr Wickers' play. Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 不管是糖衣炮弹还是什么 我都同意\NDo you know what, hustler, I think I'm going to drop that goodwill pill you just scored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然艾尔非不见他妈妈好多年\NAlthough Alfie's not seen her in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须相信他 做点准备 好的\NWell, you've got to convince her then. Make something up. Right-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 请问是威克斯夫人吗?\NHello, is that Mrs Wickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 现在应该称呼您加西亚·拉米雷斯夫人!\NSorry, currently Mrs Garcia-Ramires!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我是弗瑞泽\NYes, it's Mr Fraser here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔非他...\NAlfie's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,..出车祸了 非常严重\N..been in a horrific car crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这就是机器小钳子\NOK, so this is Robocracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个毫无希望的世界 住着一个有情绪问题的不良少年\NIn a world without hope, lived an angry maladjusted delinquent boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你 弗兰克\NThat is you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在圣诞清晨 弗兰克醒来 发现圣诞树下有个玩偶 是机器小钳子\NFrank wakes up Christmas morning, finds beneath the tree a doll, it's Robocracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你 史蒂芬\NThat's you, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节发生的奇迹 小钳子活了!\NChristmas miracle,Robocracker's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 他和这个问题男孩一起 开始了维护世界和平的正义之旅\NAnd him and the delinquent boy set about to bring peace to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,轰动英国 一夜爆红 嗅到电影学院奖的气息了吗?\NSprinkle in a couple of explosions, throw in a sex scene, bish bash bosh, who smells BAFTA?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠这部剧 你可赢不了英国电影学院奖\NYou can't win a BAFTA for a theatre show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的角色都有人了 不过谁来演反派角色...\NAll the parts are cast, except for the role of the villain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,朝鲜的暴君 金正恩\NNorth Korean despot, Kim Jong-un.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谁 谁来演这个角色呢?\NOh, who, oh, who could play that part?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我演一个大腹便便的 中年朝鲜老男人?\NYou want me to play an overweight middle-aged North Korean man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别误会 静 那是他以前的形象 现在我们不提那个\NEr, no, Jing, we're not talking about a lazy stereotype here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要塑造的是一个有血有肉 形象丰满的人物角色\NWe are talking about a three-dimensional, very rounded character,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:11:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一个胖乎乎的 特立独行的孤独者...\Na very rounded sort of, chubby oddball loner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快给我剧本\NJust give me the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,乔 你要演金正恩吗 一个闪闪发光 更为亲和的金正恩\NJoe, you are going to make a brilliant not-so-Lil' Kim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,金正恩为啥会出现在《机器小钳子》里?\NHow is Kim Jong-un in Robocracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为金正恩想抓机器人小钳子\NBecause Kim Jong-un wants to capture Robocracker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得到小钳子的心脏 制造一种导弹 他就可以摧毁世界了\Nso he can use his robotic heart to power a missile that can destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只有得到了那颗心脏 他才知道心脏并不是机械的\NOnly when he gets hold of the heart,he realises it's not robotic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一颗正常的 人类男孩的心脏\Nit's actually the heart of a real boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这再明显不过了 想想就明白了 静\NIt's actually very obvious if you think about it, Jing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 老师 好凄美的故事啊\NThank you, sir, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不干脆做莎士比亚剧呢?\NWhy can't we just do Shakespeare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,同样的理由 我也不看《质询时间》\NFor the same reason that I don't watch Question Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又无聊 也看不懂 观众还时不时就爆笑\NBecause it's boring, confusing and the audience laugh at a load of jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一卡车没几个正常人会懂的笑话\Nthat no normal person would ever understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如何来营造一种忠诚 信任又幸福的氛围呢?\NSo, how do we create a loyal, trusting, happy environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都裸体吗?\NEveryone get naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只要躺在地板上 让别人从你身上滚过去就行\NWhat we do is we all lie on the floor,and then take turns to roll over each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,选一个搭档\NPick a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我选乔\NI'll take Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,做好准备 开始滚就行了\NWhen you're ready, just over you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,马上过去了 好家伙...\NNearly there, big guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老腰!\NOh, my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\NArgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\NRem Dogg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老师到我了吗?不 不要...\NIs it my go, sir? No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我啊 老师!\NTrust me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你要滚去哪?\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我!\NTrust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我们在做一个信任实践的排演\NEr,we were just doing a trust exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道 今晚的圣诞特别节目 谁要加入呢?\NEr, I was wondering who's coming on our special outing this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,凑!抱歉 我把这事给忘了!\NOh, shit! Sorry. I forgot to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,同学们 谁想跟格老师一起去呢...\NEr, guys, do any of you want to go with Miss Gulliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还有威克斯老师 没错 还有我...\NAnd Mr Wickers. And me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,去一个可爱的 收留流浪汉的施粥场\Nto a lovely, trampy soup kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想手淫\NI'm not going tramp-wanking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有手淫的 米切尔\NEr, there's no wanking involved,Mitchell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有么?\NIs there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要对流浪汉手淫呢?\NWhy would we wank off tramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为他们取暖么?\NTo keep them warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有人愿意去吗?\NDoes anyone want to volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,罗西啊 事实就是 我们在搞一个这样的剧\NThe thing is, Rosie,er, we're kind of doing this play,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没有太多的时间去干那个\Nso we don't really have much spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我不会说苏格兰语 所以我和那些流浪汉没法儿...\NPlus, I don't speak Scottish,so me and tramps don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔非 你最好不要后悔\NAlfie, I am going to make you stick to your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我非弄这个剧不可\NWell, I'm sorry,I have to do this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,领导发话我才去\NI need to get the governors back on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕这次我是怎么都不会去了\NSo I'm afraid on this occasion I am putting my foot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不好玩么?\NIsn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你弄这儿来 你不高兴吗?\NAren't you glad I made you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,给我些巴奇 兄弟!\NGie us some Bucky, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,巴奇?是种酒\NBucky? It's alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的 你看 在施粥场我们只提供粥\NYeah, look, I'm afraid we only serve soup in this soup kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去你妈的 你个混蛋\NGet tae fuck, ya sleekit wee bastard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们点巴奇 不然你死哪儿都不知道 有钱的混球!\Ngie us some Bucky or ye'll end up in a ditch, you toff buftie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,额 这是苏格兰语的"给我些巴豆"的意思么?\NOK, is that Scottish for,"Yes, please, with croutons"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我该干吗\NOi, dinnae you be tellin' me whit tae dae!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是老大\NYou're nae the boss o' me,ya doss radge dug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱的狗狗啊!\NAh, what a lovely doggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它叫什么?\NWhat's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...\NEr...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"要是您找到我们的狗 请拨打020..."丫的 是数字\N"If found, please call 020..."Och, numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一条狗叫这种名 怪死了\NWhat an odd name to give a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不  这可不是我的狗\NNo, no, he's no' mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我从一笨蛋那偷来的 他在街上把我揍了一顿\NI stole him aff some numpty-heided bastard who tried tae gie me a doin' in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太惨了\NHow awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 那货拿着根这种棍子朝我们走过来  不过我们把他甩掉了\NAye, he came at us wi' a stick!Eh, eh! But I got it off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谁愿意和瘦骨头干架呢\NCos nae-one messes wi' Boney.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们谁要我就卖给你们\NI'll sell it tae youse if ye like,yeah, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个\NGot these an' all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,全新的喔\NBrand-new, like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老师!\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,流浪汉们不可爱吗?\NAren't tramps lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 你想要雄驴还是雌驴?\NSir, what sort of donkey do you want,a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最可爱的就行\NJust whatever looks cutest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 小钳子 若是不能随音乐起舞 我们如何消灭艾滋呢?\NBut, Robocracker, how can we cure AIDS with no music to dance to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不必担心 弗兰克 我碰巧是波诺最好的朋友!\NNever fear, Frank, because I happen to be best friends with Bono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你要拥抱他\NAnd then you hug him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不抱男人\NI'm not hugging any blokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子们 我能提点建议么?\NLads, can I gie ye a wee bit of advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把你自己想象成一块空白的画布 把你对角色的理解描摹于上\NThink of yourselves as blank canvases on to which your characters'motivations are projected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,懂我说的什么吗?\Nye ken what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 您真的了解戏剧吗?\NSorry, what do you know about drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 我不了解戏剧 你这个话都说不清楚的货\NWhat don't I know about drama, you,ya jobby-jabber!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 虽然我现在看起来是个脏兮兮的流浪汉!\NAh ken maybe no' to look at me, right,but I huvnae always been a dirty Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是很久之前 我可是我那代最有名的演员之一\NSee back in the day, I was one of the most famous actors in my generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你说得出 我就做得到\NYou name it, I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,企业宣传片《塔格特》里面的小角色 也给皇家莎士比亚剧团跑过龙套...\NCorporate videos, part in Taggart,even done a run at the RSC...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...之后我的演艺事业就一蹶不振 还不如卖驴毛的\N..and then the work dried up,worse than a swamp donkey's fud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,闹事 活成这副鬼样子 还得靠行乞才能弄点酒钱\NAh hit the streets, living rough,begging for booze money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,闹事 活成这副鬼样子 还得靠行乞才能弄点酒钱\NAh hit the streets, living rough,begging for booze money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,之后就更惨不忍睹了\NAnd then, aye,then things got really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你演过主角吗?\NDid you get into heroin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我演过《圣橡镇少年》\NI got into Hollyoaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 是 赫加蒂夫人啊 晚上好啊\NAh, Mrs Hegarty. Hi. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!博纳海德(傻瓜)先生真高兴你能来\NAh! Mr Bonehead,so pleased you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧在哪?我要喝一杯\NWhere's the bar? I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁请了他们啊?\NAh, who invited those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我觉得你会喜欢\NI did. I thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们都无家可归 不过他们稍微花点心思 注意下形象也行啊\NI get that they're homeless, right,but they could have made a bit of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的那个家伙连鞋都没穿\NThat guy over there's not even got any shoes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我提到的\NNow this is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一个稍微努力下就改头换面的流浪汉\NA tramp that's made a little bit of bloody effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 虽然你还留着这些破海绵 不过起码你找到了件好衣服!\NYeah, sure you've kept the old clunge sponge, but at least you've found yourself a suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你洗得干干净净\NYou've had a wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且...好像一位领导\NAnd... you're a governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈德赛先生\NMr Hardside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在想起来了...真的非常抱歉 我希望你今晚玩得开心\NI've just remembered now...I'm awfully sorry, I hope you have a wonderful evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,威克斯夫人正在盖特威克机场\NMrs Wickers is at Gatwick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么解释她儿子在遭遇了十车连撞事故 又突然活蹦乱跳的呢?\NHow are we going to explain her son's sudden recovery from a ten-car pileup?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有两个选择 一说是圣诞节奇迹 二只能说艾尔非老师残了\NOur options are: a) Christmas miracle or two) actually maim Alf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我比你聪明 老师\NNo, I'm one step ahead of you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸有很多设备啊 以前装颈部扭伤弄赔偿金的时候\NMe Dad's got a load of these left over from making whiplash claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时想攒钱买辆车 太机智了!\NHe's saving up for a car.Brill-cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,威克斯先生!快走!\NMr Wickers! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,得让大家都到里面去 艾尔非 快 把这个套上\NWe need to get everyone inside. Alf,quickly, you need to put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你的安全着想\NElf 'n' safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗?\NGet it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不过说真的 解说员在全程解说的时候也可能受伤的\NBut seriously, narrators can get hurt doing all that reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\NArgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,愿上帝保佑 祝好运 真主至大\NGod bless, Mazeltov, Allah Akbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子王。。。\NArsene Wenger,balls-bis hiya waya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,温馨提示 本校有定点厕所设施\NLittle bit of housekeeping, this school does have toilet facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我主要是指后面那位先生 我看到你了\NThat one was mainly aimed at the gentleman at the back.I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹!\NGet tae fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐吖 亲\NAnd a very merry Christmas to you,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,由威克斯老师为您献上\NOver to you, Mr Wickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太兴奋哦\NDrop it like it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是圣诞节前夜\NIt was the night before Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,屋子里死气沉沉的 连老鼠都不活跃\Nand all through the house not a creature was stirring, not even a mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,从我身上下来 你个贱人\NOh, get off me, you bell-end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,主角是弗兰克 一个十岁大的男孩\NOur hero is Frank,a ten-year-old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么没穿演出服?\NWhy aren't you wearing your costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不穿紧身裤的 亲\NI'm not wearing tights, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克的父母一贫如洗 今天是没什么礼物可得了\NOh! Frank's parents are poor,no presents today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,除非... 听!\Nunless... hark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看这是什么?圣诞老人驾着麋鹿 滑着雪橇来了!\NWhat is this? It is Santa with reindeer and sleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,驾 驾 驾!\N"Ho ho ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"我要带给弗兰克圣诞礼物" 圣诞老人如是说\N"I'll fetch Frank's presents,"Santa did say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他捋了捋胡子 从雪橇上下来\Nas he stroked on his beard and got out of his sleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在轮椅上呢 蠢货!\NI'm in a wheelchair, dickhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一头麋鹿去取礼物 圣诞老人还呆在雪橇上\NAs one of his reindeer went to fetch the present whilst Santa stayed put in his sleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去\NLet me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我喘不过气来了!天黑了\NI can't breathe!Day turned to night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天又亮了\NAnd then night turned to day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道我有起床气么?\NWhy did I bother getting out of bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克大声说 声如洪钟\NFrank did say, very loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去! - 够了!\NLet me out! This is shite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么?\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在树下...我不能呼吸了!\NBut under the tree...I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,..这是什么 弗兰克默默地观察着!\N..What's this that Frank spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是机器小钳子\NIt's Robocracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克简直不敢相信自己的眼睛!\NFrank can't believe his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧?\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个破箱子里 我快不能呼吸了!\NI couldn't breathe in that box!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克的祈祷 圣诞老人听到了\NFrank makes a wish that Santa does hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"让这个玩偶活过来\N"Make this doll come to life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"我就不躲在自行车棚后面喝啤酒了\N"and I'll stop drinking beer behind the bike sheds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"不再欺负弱小\N"and being a massive bully
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"在学校听老师的话 不惹老师生气\N"and constantly going on about how one of his teachers got bummed at boarding school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便提一下 唯一一个 碰过我的屁股的人是我的朋友阿提克斯·霍伊 比如 有次\NFYI the only person that's ever touched my bum is my friend Atticus Hoye, like, once,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在伊甸园计划的时候 只有那次\Nwhen we were at the Eden Project, this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦!\NGay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,米契尔 这是你自己的表演 你可不能起哄\NMitchell,you can't heckle your own show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克和他的朋友有一个梦想 他们要将助人进行到底\NFrank and his friend set out on a quest, until they'd helped everyone,they would not rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这坨破东西是谁写的?\NWho wrote this shite?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我屁股里出来的东西 构思都比这个强\NI've seen jobbies come out of my arse with better structure than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\NArgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要!这是我的个人秀\NNo! This is my solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,戴着这么个破头盔 我什么都看不到!老师!\NI can't see anything in this stupid helmet! Oi, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,米契尔 到这儿来!\NMitchell, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太不专业了 快穿上你的裤子!\NIt's so unprofessional.Pull your trousers up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开!\NGet off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,米契尔 住手!\NMitchell, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快滚开 你个二货!\NGet off. You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,中场休息!\NInterval!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,同时 在耶路撒冷...\NMeanwhile, in Jerusalem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用我的枪占领这块圣地 你个整天撸的货\NI called shotgun on the Holy Land,you wanktard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快滚开吧!耶路撒冷是我的 你个眼瞎的!\NOh, do one!Jerusalem is mine, you Jap's eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你弄起来 放到茶叶袋里扔了\NI'm going to pin you down and teabag ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧 把轮子放这儿来\NCome on, get the cogs in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,剧本里根本没有\NNot even in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是机器人小钳子来了\NBut here comes Robocracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他想到了一个让两方都不吃亏的办法 一城两治\NHe has an idea of a neutral shared city in a two-state solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他将通过舞蹈来表达自己的主意\Nwhich he will explain through the medium of expressive dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是和谐之舞!\NIt's now time for the Tolerance Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没错小钳子让大家一团和气\NYeah, Robocracker brings everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,奇迹啊奇迹!\NIt's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,疼啊 弄我眼里去了\NAh, it's in my bloody eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就是奇迹!\NIt's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,本是心疼迷失的结局\NThey've put an end to heartache and loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们的勇士必须要解决祸首了\Nbut now our brave pair must take on the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会抓到你的 机器小钳子!\NI'll get you, Robocracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你别做梦了 我可是个正常的人类男孩!\NNo, you shan't for I am a real boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的罗密欧在哪?\NWhere is my Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 一定是毒药结果了他的生命\NPoison, I see,hath been his timeless end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要吻着你的嘴唇...\NI will kiss thy lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这上面还留着一些毒液\Nhappily some poison yet doth hang on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的嘴唇还是温暖的\NThy lips are warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让我死了吧!\NLet me die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 毫无希望 没有办法\NAlas there's no hope, no treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,无药可救 小钳子的生命就这样消逝了 弗兰克向他告别 深情相...\Nno drug, as Robo's life fades away,Frank bids adieu with a hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,相拥!\NHug!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,剧本里写的是拥抱\NIn the script it says hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看发生了什么?\NBut what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小钳子重获新生 最终化身成为了一个真正的男孩!\NRobocracker has been reincarnated and finally he's a real boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大结局!\NThe end!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真棒 从这边出去\NCome on, you lot. Out you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还不去休息室吗?\NHaven't you got homes to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,演得真好\NWell done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谬赞了\NOh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,凭良心说\NFair do's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.55,0:24:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你的讲述很感人\NYour narrative arc was engaging,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但真正深入人心的 是观众对\Nbut the pleasurable representations dinnae depend on the likeness of the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.79,0:24:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所塑造形象的喜爱度 你懂我的意思么 蠢货?\Nthat they are portraying. You know what I mean, ya minging bag o' shite?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谨遵教诲 下次我会注意的\NOh, I'll bear that in mind for next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我勇敢的小宝贝啊!\NMy brave little baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.63,0:24:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.95,0:24:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来我真是太意外了\NI can't believe you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一听说你出事 我们就赶来了\NWe came as soon as we heard about the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.71,0:24:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出事?是我...\NThe accident? Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,..忘记邀请她 那个意外!\N..forgetting to put her invite in the fricking post, that accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.27,0:25:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你邀请了我妈?好吧 其实是米契尔阁下的主意\NYou invited my mum? Well, it was Mr Mitchell's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.23,0:25:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太感谢我 迪克斯\NDon't go soppy on me, Dickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.59,0:25:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你哈维尔叔叔也在这儿!\NAnd Uncle Javier is here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.99,0:25:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒 哈维尔叔叔啊\NGreat, Uncle Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.43,0:25:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直挺想他的\NI've really missed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小男子汉\NOh, me valiente hombre.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.95,0:25:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔非 哈维尔叔叔真为你骄傲\NAlfie,Uncle Javier is so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定会查出 谁把你害得这么惨 我们一定会追究到底\NWe're going to find the men who put you in this chair, and we're going to make them pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.07,0:25:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有人能阻止费兰度·托利斯欺负我么?\NCan someone stop Fernando Torres trying' to bum me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.03,0:25:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哈维尔 那不是艾尔非\NJavier, that's not Alfie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.79,0:25:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个才是...您好\NThis is... Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.87,0:25:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.67,0:25:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道是你\NI knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.15,0:25:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚是小玩笑而已\NIt was a little joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.67,0:25:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 哈维尔叔叔 这就是我跟你们提过的女孩\NEr, Mum, Javier, this is the girl I've been telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.23,0:25:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,罗西\NRosie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.35,0:25:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,见到您很荣幸\NIt's so nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.79,0:26:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你会留下来过圣诞节吗?\NSo will you be staying for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.67,0:26:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的艾尔非小宝贝儿身体好转之前 我们会一直呆在这儿\NWe are going to stay until little Alfie is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.43,0:26:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好赶快去艾尔非的教室 有圣诞大餐喔!\NWe better head to Alfie's classroom for Christmas dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.35,0:26:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要吃烤鸡!\NWho wants turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.95,0:26:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有收到西汉姆联队的门票?\NSo did you get the West Ham ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.03,0:26:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是你给我的?\NOh, you got me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.95,0:26:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想去么?\NSo do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.03,0:26:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\NAll right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 那代表不了什么 比如 算了...\NI mean, it don't mean nothing or, like, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.11,0:26:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就别想那场表演了 亲爱的\NYou can give up that act now, babes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,猜猜我对那些做了什么?什么?\NGuess what I done with them crackers?What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.55,0:26:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,互相交换\NSwapped the jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.19,0:26:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有个问题要问您\NHere's one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.71,0:26:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,百分之九十的人都喜欢什么?\NWhat do nine out of ten people enjoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.67,0:26:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,群...\NGang ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.19,0:26:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喔哦\NRawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.11,0:26:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一头狮子\NAn impression of a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.79,0:27:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 女士们 先生们\NExcuse me, ladies and gents.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要到走廊里一下 借用一下你们的厕所\NEr, just going to go down the hallway to only use your lavatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.23,0:27:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NEr, so, thank youse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.75,0:27:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 博纳海德的生活终于步入正轨了\NAw, Bonehead's got his life back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.95,0:27:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的剧真的帮了他呢\NYour play really helped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.23,0:27:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得 我们给他看了大点的那个照片 真的很棒\NI just think it's great that we've been able to show him the bigger picture. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.27,0:27:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我给你准备了 一个小礼物\NOh, I got you a tiny silly little present thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.03,0:27:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,米契尔 那头驴没一起来么?\NMitchell,how's that donkey coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.95,0:27:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一个小时前 它就从罗马尼亚来了\NIt arrived from Romania about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.83,0:27:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\NOh, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.11,0:27:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到证书了吗?什么证书?\NHave you got the certificate? What certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.03,0:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这里有只半驴\NRight, here's half the donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.67,0:27:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,另一半我交给厨房了\NThe rest I gave to the kitchens.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.83,0:27:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你自己吃不上\NI figured you couldn't eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.47,0:27:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔非雷德 这肉真好吃 嫩滑多汁啊\NAlfredo, this meat is lovely!It's so bloody moist!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.19,0:28:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,布 布勃莱!\NB-Buble!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.99,0:28:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们可以天天听这个CD 一直到圣诞节喽?\NDoes this mean we can listen to it every day until Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.19,0:28:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的真的爱死你了\NI guess I must really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.15,0:28:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,老师硬了!\NSir's got a boner!
